## Phase 4: Agent Collaboration Optimization ✅

### What Was Built
lib/collaboration-manager.ts — Enhanced agent collaboration system

### Key Features
Collaboration graph — Maps agent relationships and dependencies
Routing intelligence — ML-based routing with confidence scoring
Autonomy levels — 3-tier autonomy system (1=fully autonomous, 2=draft+review, 3=consult only)
Handoff protocol — Agent handoff tracking and pattern detection
Conflict resolution — Escalation paths for agent disagreements

### Files Changed
[TABLE:2×2]

### Test Results
✅ Collaboration graph loaded with 14 agents
✅ Routing confidence calculation works
✅ Agent autonomy levels configured
✅ Team chat route updated with collaboration features

