## Key Improvements Delivered

### 1. Automated SIP Triggering
Before: Manual flag reading in SESSION.md
After: Automated notification in each agent's MEMORY.md + scheduled execution

Impact:
✅ No more missed SIP distillations
✅ Agents aware of their own SIP schedule
✅ One-click SIP execution via API

### 2. Memory Management
Before: Only session log capped at 50 entries
After: Multi-section caps, compression, and archiving

Impact:
✅ Consistent file sizes across all agents
✅ Faster file reads and writes
✅ Full history preserved in archives

### 3. Dependency Decoupling
Before: 31 files referenced SESSION.md directly
After: Centralized SessionManager service

Impact:
✅ Single source of truth
✅ Easier maintenance and updates
✅ Better error handling and validation

### 4. Enhanced Collaboration
Before: Simple keyword-based routing
After: ML-enhanced routing with autonomy levels

Impact:
✅ Better agent matching to queries
✅ Clear autonomy boundaries
✅ Improved collaboration success rate

