## Agent Behavior Analysis

### Independence Level: HIGH ✅
Each agent maintains:
Own MEMORY.md — Complete session history
Own SKILLS.md — Distilled patterns & protocols
Own personality — Distinct operating philosophy
Domain expertise — Clear responsibility boundaries

### Collaboration Pattern: ORCHESTRATED ✅

Current Collaboration Flow:
User Query → Intent Classifier → Specialist Selection
Parallel Briefing → 1-2 specialists brief simultaneously
CEO Synthesis → Marcus merges briefings into unified response
Autonomy Check → Each agent's autonomy level validated

Agent Call Patterns:
Explicit Calls: /api/brand-intelligence (Kai → Lena)
Routing System: /api/team-chat (parallel specialist briefings)
Pipeline Pattern: Sequential agent dependencies

### When Agents Call Other Agents:
Data → Content: Kai (analytics) → Lena (brand) for content briefs
Parallel Briefings: 1-2 specialists → CEO synthesis
Handoff Protocol: Agent can request assistance from another

