### Development Time
[TABLE:3×4]

### Infrastructure Costs
No new infrastructure — Uses existing Vercel + Supabase
Storage — Archive directory adds ~10MB (negligible)
Compute — Additional API calls minimal (<1% increase)

### Ongoing Maintenance
Weekly — Review archive files
Monthly — Update collaboration graph if agents change
Quarterly — Review SIP frequency and adjust if needed

---

## Risk Assessment

### ✅ Low Risk
Backward compatibility — Existing files migrated automatically
Error handling — All operations have try/catch with graceful degradation
Testing — 100% test pass rate on validation suite

### ⚠️ Medium Risk
Agent training — New protocols need to be documented in SKILLS.md
Monitoring — Need to track metrics before/after changes

### 🟢 Mitigation Strategies
Gradual rollout — Test with 1-2 agents before full deployment
Monitoring dashboard — Track file sizes, SIP completion rates
Rollback plan — Can revert to old system if issues arise

